            <title>Student and Instructor Resources</title>
            <para id="fs-idm1443621424">We’ve compiled additional resources for both students and instructors, including Getting Started Guides, [other resources dependent on book]. Instructor resources require a verified instructor account, which can be requested on your openstax.org log-in. Take advantage of these resources to supplement your OpenStax book.</para>
