        <section id="fs-idm1166021776">
            <title>Partner Resources</title>
            <para id="fs-idm361867408">OpenStax Partners are our allies in the mission to make high-quality learning materials affordable and accessible to students and instructors everywhere. Their tools integrate seamlessly with our OpenStax titles at a low cost. To access the partner resources for your text, visit your book page on openstax.org.</para>
        </section>
